## From https://jasonstitt.com/gitignore-whitelisting-patterns

# 1. Ignore everything
*

# 2. But descend into directories
!*/

# 3. Allow specific files and file extensions
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!.dockerignore
!.vscode/settings.json
!requirements.txt
!Dockerfile
!*.py
!*.md
!*.tf
!*.yaml
!.devcontainer/*.json
!.vscode/*.json
!.env_template

# 4. Block some directories and files
*.git
**/*env
**/.venv
**/TMP
**/_archive
**/output
**/analysis
**/.terraform